    "name": "The Atlantic - Hide Sidebar Elements",
    "description": "Hide certain promo elements on The Atlantic sidebar (related content, sidebar elements, etc.) and article area (top profile, share buttons, etc.)\r\nNot including adboxes to hide, because I prefer to give the magazine those ad views. There are other ways to hide ads if that is your preference.",
